{"tid":787453,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"有個人問我朋友借左九萬蚊,之後","createTime":"2018-08-20T16:06:10.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-20T16:22:28.000Z","uid":60438,"like":0,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"4f699a5f740f942dedf0914d637996d472007deb","tid":787453,"uid":60438,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-20T16:06:10.000Z","msg":"有個人(A)問我朋友借左九萬蚊之後一直唔見人,之前A都簽咗借據表示會同意係6月25日或之前還住部份錢比我朋友,但直至6月30號一直冇過數記錄,咁我朋友就去A公司搵佢,A既上司見到我朋友就警告我朋友唔好黎搞事,叫佢地私底下解決,唔好係公司搞啲咁既野,而且A既上司又話唔知A幾時收工,咁我朋友只好走 ,走左之後一直打A電話都冇人聽,最近直頭熄埋機,WhatsApp又已讀不回<br />\n請問大家應該可以點幫我朋友？<br />\nps:A係一間韓國S開頭既電子公司(香港)做手機customer service<br />\n我都有幫我朋友做左啲research 關於入稟小額錢債,但上限最多只能5萬<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/20/232013_a7964bd774ee4d9ad6b1f872e17e1a70.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F20%2F232013_a7964bd774ee4d9ad6b1f872e17e1a70.jpg&h=6bcc22fb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/21/000540_338b7bc398da9a9caa706533b45c535f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F21%2F000540_338b7bc398da9a9caa706533b45c535f.jpg&h=7c6d77f9&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"68874b09ebf4aec32cc402209958d9d13a6fd6c2","tid":787453,"uid":144466,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-20T16:20:20.000Z","msg":"想做樓主朋友<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f80342699988c917f2c9b7215f4dd836372e7499","tid":787453,"uid":72228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-20T16:22:28.000Z","msg":"手字都經典囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n小學雞咁款"}]}